Notes
===================

In order to compile the Newton module, you will need sys87.Newton. Get it from,
http://github.com/system87/sys87.mod

In order for the D3D driver to work properly, follow these directions,
https://github.com/kfprimm/maxb3d/wiki/BRL.DXGraphics-and-BRL.D3D9Max2D-Tweak
